title: Test
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of respondents, with a total of 5 data points.
Overall Share of respondents has increased over the Year
Share of respondents is rapidly increasing from I_don't_watch_TV to More_than_20_hours, and lastly rapidly decreasing from More_than_20_hours to 5_hours_or_less.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year I_don't_watch_TV and More_than_20_hours.
Max Share of respondents about 39.0 was recorded at Year More_than_20_hours
Min Share of respondents about 2.0 was recorded at Year I_don't_watch_TV
